# Gmail OAuth2 credentials (Desktop app type).
# Setup: https://console.cloud.google.com → new project → enable Gmail API →
# create "OAuth 2.0 Client ID" (Desktop) → copy the id/secret here →
# run `npm run gmail:auth` once to mint token.json. See GMAIL_SETUP.md.
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-google-client-secret

# Optional email filters consumed by MailListener's EmailFilterConfig (a caller
# would parse these and pass them to the constructor):
# EMAIL_MAX_AGE_HOURS=24
# EMAIL_ALLOWED_DOMAINS=example.com,company.org
# EMAIL_BLOCKED_DOMAINS=spam.com,newsletter.net
# EMAIL_BLOCKED_SENDERS=noreply@spam.com
# EMAIL_SUBJECT_BLOCKLIST=/unsubscribe/i,/^Newsletter:/
